channel.title: Silab Items
channel.description:
OK, when u go to a shop that has silab items (i.e.-member shop sells d boots + god sword) the god sword + d boots appear as seeds and there names are null but it costs same amount as usual. And i have a command for silab client-::silab, what it does is give u all the new silab items, so i type it and it gives me the silab items except they're seeds and their names are null....also im using project czar server and CSK client...so like for example, i go to member shop and trade store owner and it shows the items then at the bottom where the silab items are it has these seeds and there item names are null, so i value the null and its says dragon boots:are 132K and god sword:132M...although when i spawn the items no problem regular items. any solutions?
/Thanks Dominate

They’re the right items, but the item pic is a seed,it’s name is null and you can’t equip it.Please don’t post if you don’t have a reasonable answer.
